message: What’s more reliable then the UNESCO site saying she’s a philanthropist? Hardly any articles claim she’s an actress, you’re not considered an actress for doing a docu series playing yourself, once in your life. Most public figures do TV. She has a full career in philanthropy.
Is Malala an actress just for doing TV too? No! She is an activist and philanthropist. The subject has done a full career in philanthropy.
UNESCO Mahatma Gandhi Institute of Education for Peace and Sustainable Development page verifies her occupations.  https://mgiep.unesco.org/council-for-kindnessmatters

Her occupations as a Philanthropist, speaker and author can be found in the UNESCO page https://mgiep.unesco.org/council-for-kindnessmatters. Both her clothing line and NGO are registered in the Mexican government web, type them in here: https://acervomarcas.impi.gob.mx:8181/marcanet/
